\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114174909J1kri4udZ6lxEUf3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114174913nlceobVfgsuzPMEa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499135\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114174916nhrecx3psoDLYO6w.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500883\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114174941XYzKHZRFJ49DAUM1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499590\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114174920PeGFrvsQYWAN810h.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500818\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114174923KV1UehoTNyn38D25.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498221\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811141749279a4FLj2YlsoNVUAn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114174932grbBUpz1PiRtQqwy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114174934ArtkFXWhuERKDL8I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499214\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114175503kdhwVToBrfsU92gE.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498717\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://nowre.com/sneaker/372949/air-fear-of-god-1-guanfangtupianshichufashouriqidingwei-12-yue-15-ri/\" rel=\"nofollow\">耐克 Air Fear of God 1 官方图片正式发布，定价 395 美元，12 月 15 日发售。</a></strong><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114173915Z7YeTz4FxNDw2SQn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599700\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811141739167PHW3CRLslM1Ezdb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114173911v2LpGmlJ6CygkTcx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599700\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201811141739144AExG29YIJNuXZCa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599700\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114173915Yma9FgQWur7lz5TP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.599700\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114173914YsZdM48IJq0wjkAr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://qz.com/1460552/polish-artists-depiction-of-europes-political-anxieties-goes-viral/\" rel=\"nofollow\">波兰艺术家 Ada Zielińska 的一张摄影作品引起热议</a></strong>。<br></p><p>在这张作品中，一位外国游客靠在舒适的酒店房间里望向窗外。从窗口可以看见城市广场上沸腾的游行活动。在“一战”停战百周年、波兰国内民族主义抬头的背景下，艺术家说她无意讨论政治，只想展现“两个波兰”。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10155976516947507&amp;set=a.83650912506&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" rel=\"nofollow\">一位 Facebook 用户评论道</a>：“这张照片恰当描述了如今一个个体被歇斯底里的群体裹挟时的感受”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114170602diwgRBqXNUJD7LVb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.563043\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/makena-mambo-a-part-of-me-photography-121118\" rel=\"nofollow\">肯尼亚裔美国摄影师&nbsp;Makena Mambo 的个人摄影项目“A Part of Me”</a></strong>。<br></p><p>拍摄对象是居住在肯尼亚、与 Mambo 家族相熟的一对双胞胎 Emily 和 Miriam Kinyanjui。摄影师说，她想将自身文化背景注入常见的杂志时尚摄影中。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114170502aQmd9JuP5trIwAMz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114170325o06hndCPx2gYI58i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114170327pK6XFxdaJg8bfsy3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.498619\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114170317PZVHQK7OaRkNnIB9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114170319nKv03u2CTqwikIBL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114170322YxXMZR1KfySjAcPt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114170329KMgAUX4PVO9ucSde.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20181114170330y3CGBkjRtHm8WXe6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div>"}